  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ac5fa56a-d18f-4cd0-98cb-598645b3c4d9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8a8062b4-82cd-4698-b8a4-3c7360e80e86\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-37a13374-dba9-411e-8c96-b102f76da7be\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Package Paper Ⅰ</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0c6b155e-dd75-4c5c-bd4e-7cef7077dc60\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3d183e8d-c2cb-48a0-a134-de84d8e24c93\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-96f8f6db-5b67-4e5b-9494-c50670369221\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1811af62-d7ad-4543-91fd-51ba0543dc41\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>종이는 인쇄의 분류 중에 가장 중요한 요소입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2bf1557c-6105-4d2f-8deb-57545f946e4f\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-678c4159-33de-4c8f-8302-fac6a2757c0b\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>특히 패키지는 종이의 영향을 많이 받습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7283c232-abdc-401f-a362-82521696b4d7\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8b8ae02f-f0a5-44c0-9b55-ea7636995651\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>우리가 흔히 사용하는 명함 종이는</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-45080f76-0f26-4093-9057-2bac08d151f3\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-652ce20c-682f-46d2-a52f-28e4da8e95cf\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>반누브, 휘라레, 아르떼 등 우리는</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-12e8e259-4eab-4f96-b76b-bb6971e6c122\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-688368be-fb56-4221-ac06-f60845d73215\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>대부분 명함 종이는 알고 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8d12b913-4e71-4a84-9d79-9721a894e9a9\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-641682f8-6ef5-4fc1-9116-828c7a263272\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-27a489c9-8985-4432-a923-a78d4560f459\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-93474d48-6482-41c1-9f42-64eba729d20e\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>하지만 박스 종이는</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3c41c215-7877-45f2-83b7-7b44d1a6e1ba\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6091bb1d-7770-4706-be3a-51d81cd88642\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>일반적인 고객분들이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1cf3ffdf-6b2c-4873-b8e2-ec01a7cfcc3c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-11b8d1d1-fb88-4237-8d27-5340724aebec\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>잘 알지 못합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8b135204-6292-4234-8fe9-5124a04ed873\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-44378a78-8a94-4834-b1c9-69646752ed05\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6832e857-6796-4e38-8784-7dc7fdfc274e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ca51ee38-9ad4-4838-b090-b8ea4db5d58c\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>아이보리(IV)와 마닐라지가</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0a0461eb-b372-4b6e-be2c-e4f514067635\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f8a4556d-5f48-4ec5-90ed-d22c5a3faf9a\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>어떻게 다른지?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8fb5b17c-2705-461d-827f-2600eae07cc5\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5eeb2711-332d-4f3c-832b-ab2fc70d9b14\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>많이 사용하는 CCP지는</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-74bd6584-8b51-4350-87bc-35aba8edfde3\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3df9d494-104c-4a8a-95ce-4c6e7e268f31\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>어떤 특성이 있는지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f50d36a3-99e7-49c1-8ecf-6dcd509977d3\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-50fc8038-7df5-4664-8b31-d1203bdb3180\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>또한 지질이 거친 느낌의</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7d50b31c-cc22-4f23-b5b8-6ee381228a17\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e9b9f284-8b98-49a7-b3d1-f445ca9749ce\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>패키지 종이는 없는지? 등에</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9693bdf8-479d-4dd3-9c9e-7743021b1213\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-85156f81-23c1-4e31-865c-3baa755670b6\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>대해 알아보겠습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e505f356-c7c5-411c-9f78-976392c51d62\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223745219068/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-1f07239f-f974-4427-ba47-68f691adeae4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223745219068/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d6c73ce7-4daf-426e-8c40-870b0ba7d23d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f7a95f77-3ccb-488b-bdce-fbdf1f8d00e5\" style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>가장 사랑받는 패키지, 박스 종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6d7bad9f-5064-47a4-92b9-e8b255c844e9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-58be29d9-a76a-4787-866e-3609cef761da\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">우리가 사용하는 패키지 종이 중에 가장 많이 사랑받는 종이가 있습니다. 이 말은 여러 가지 의미를 내포하고 있습니다. 단가적으로 메리트를 말할 수 있고 종이 두께를 고려할 수도 있습니다. 또한 일반적으로 코팅처리가 되므로 코팅이 사전에 처리된 종이도 있습니다. 크게 보면 3가지로 나눠 설명드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d750cc52-9560-4f32-8f3a-71ec9e16349d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-881720e3-f618-4bbb-975f-30cb01aefd06\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-346c0a32-0c3c-4fdf-9b5f-9a95c60a72fe\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a5289394-6016-488a-b171-b694c2d6fa9f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>마닐라지</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dbb3da60-73e4-4193-977c-cad0ba8a7c47\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ebdf9560-0667-4a95-81d1-7516d53cdc57\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">목재 섬유에 마닐라 섬유를 섞어 만든 종이. 마닐라 지라는 이름은 필리핀 원산의 마닐라 삼에서 유래된 것이다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6fbf977d-477f-4c19-a122-b35064f50e4b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-be52a67e-8b22-4359-a96e-3cac651016f4\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">원래 마닐라지는 밝은 황갈색 종이로 매우 질기고 가볍고 수분에도 강해서 서류 봉투나 편지 봉투, 소포의 포장지, 설탕같이 습기에 약한 상품의 외부 포장에 널리 쓰였다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2bcf3a74-d5fe-4595-8b6d-b8d50eebede2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4080423a-553a-44bf-b884-ab7814c29be2\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">현재는 대부분 백색으로 코팅된 종이를 말한다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d8ace34a-ee60-4ac9-8487-2a7b2033239c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-bf275fe0-6295-4e8f-b8ad-61c5ea43f0e9\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">포장 박스용이나 표면이 매끄러워 칼라 옵셋인쇄하기 좋아 책이나 공책의 표지에도 널리 쓰인다. 크라프트지(소위 시멘트 포대 종이) 나 마분지와는 다르다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6e2ca927-08d3-48a2-81c8-959183cbc9b5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e362af05-c66c-4671-83a7-c7d18a7f24b4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-54d7d962-5be8-488e-b10d-574e15d37855\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-36d79f7b-85fc-4abd-b9e5-8cfe9eef4bcb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">마닐라 삼은 Abacá(학명: Musa Textilis) 파초과에 속하는 식물로 바나나의 친척이다.\\</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-09b0505d-b598-48a2-8fbb-a67457a4437a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f909caab-5e93-40df-a2dd-bbad042bdcfa\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">주로 섬유질을 가공해서 쓰이는데 매우 질기고 긴 섬유로 햇빛이나 물이나 마찰에 강해 과거에는 범선의 돛줄 등</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f66881e8-f1c7-4683-8bcc-9d6e2471a706\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-209ec2b1-685c-4ba3-a6d2-3bfb3695321d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">각종 선박용, 중량물 고박등 운송용, 등산용 등 각종 밧줄을 만드는데</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b655383b-92b4-4a6f-bc04-f19debdc5642\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d633a6f5-8c34-4f17-8c91-602d3e4023d2\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">널리 쓰였으나 지금은 나일론으로 거의 대체되었다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fe44fa8a-e521-49b5-b994-d6d55da96b67\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-edc1eae6-6ba6-4713-b524-30585a3745ff\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3d0c4510-3841-4a53-ae73-3944e51b88f8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4ec17090-9f0c-46f5-adef-b06ca0ced8a4\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">비닐로 덮여 있어 일반 종이보다 훨씬 튼튼하며 약간의 방수 기능도 있어서 책 표지 등에 많이 쓰인다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a498f1f9-a155-4cde-a117-8abb8f771228\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-31d8daf2-deb7-440d-9559-e15b3c5d4e62\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">비닐의 두께가 다양한데 두꺼운 비닐이 입혀진 것은 책 표지에 주로 쓰며 얇은 비닐이 입혀진 것[1]은 일반 종이만큼이나 잘 쓰인다.</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-277d7b63-34a3-483f-8823-d4b7449aa9d0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-80ac3d20-fe8b-481e-b766-d1a11001121c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">발췌 : 나무위키</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-627671fe-9dcf-4176-9e32-3d2e57510c3c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fd4c98f9-5204-4b0b-af88-792aa285f335\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-70836df4-6295-4e3f-8eda-fb31a7122f9e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-403c4ffc-fb07-4fc2-8454-5b2d43ef7b11\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">마닐라 종이는 일반적으로 단가를 중요시하는 패키지 용기에 많이 사용합니다. 뒷면은 마분지처럼 거칠게 처리되어 있어서 단면 인쇄용으로 만 사용되며 500g 기준 아이보리에 비해 약 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-07ede957-c90f-468c-9ad7-27bb1f88df02\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>76% 정도 저렴</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-75d0719a-feb1-4b53-87b2-a962298e8f10\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-029f96a3-0dfe-45ff-906f-268d3f5bdfa8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223745219068/002.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-352efef8-e455-418d-9e93-20da9d63a40e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223745219068/003.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0c0d7db4-b598-417d-8f69-05269b139fc4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c61bd087-16fb-46d9-8069-d189690cd3ab\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ba8241f1-510a-406b-80c1-fa1280d62074\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>마닐라 종이의</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1777f597-fa56-4453-a6ee-0aa81d30dad3\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> 특징은 저렴하면서 단면 인쇄로서 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2273c95f-e8f0-49ad-8107-e4e812ed372f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>포장의 의미를 두고 있는 종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fa6d457f-d0bb-48c0-95cf-c78db5e1a8ae\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">라고 설명드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-64ae6fda-e237-4b4d-a631-f7d18249ff80\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d5461817-4d56-4a2e-b323-4939bb60cb35\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b6094a93-1c0b-4e91-8c89-c430082ca020\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-46c88ccf-def0-4c9e-a49d-472f59fa08bd\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">· 색상 : 백색 / 후면 회색</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-49249c62-0804-40c5-baec-bcc9a84d738a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-afa33ca3-be42-4853-9eb3-4e72de24dcdf\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">· 평량 : 180g, 240g, 260g, 280g, 300g, 350g, 400g, 450g, 500g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c4a1b216-5d1a-4561-b833-eaedd406d480\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-32b57406-4277-4223-8678-56d160717fd5\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">· 용도 : 식품 가공식품, 생활용품, 의류/잡화, 완구, 제약회사 포장재 등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9ad67c95-03a7-4831-ba74-a7a80a6d8e47\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6a6c9225-c9ca-4c50-b817-3aeb88983670\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-039d68f3-3386-4969-a9b2-2f6f3a220d61\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2f3c2103-9a24-4035-8eff-f0907ba3a256\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>· 특징 : 이 종이는 단가를 가장 우선시합니다. 일반적으로 저렴하게 단가가 중요하게 차지하는 제품인 경우 이 종이를 선호합니다. 사전에 언급했듯이 일반 종이보다 약 75% 이상 저렴합니다. 일반적인 식품용기 중에 마닐라 종이가 가장 많으며 포장에 의미를 두는 경우 이 종이를 선택하세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8e7d1656-9f26-4f27-b511-05493f64c515\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-abdf763e-d04b-4eb0-bf8d-fc7cc8810353\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a262f588-6a27-41e3-acf8-9b182f4acc5c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f24e569b-59c6-4eba-86fe-4997d1b96011\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>아이보리</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-21394172-3f17-4408-972f-e004602a30e0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d60bef4a-1326-4d9c-b0d5-159cd05bf025\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">표면과 후면층에 표백 펄프를 부착하고 중간층에 재생펄프(고지)를 사용하여 만들어진 백색 후면을 가진 제품입니다. 제과, 의약품, 의류 등의 고급 포장재, 일반 파일용 표지 등에 사용되는 제품입니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a2878bdc-1d34-4139-8a81-ac927715de02\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fc16c0da-0d59-454d-b501-188024d3cce8\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">재활용 원료를 90% 이상 함유한 제품입니다.</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aa4e76c0-a209-4d5c-98c5-3b7e65892329\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e952bf62-14c1-42e9-9197-02b6237e7687\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">발췌 : 한솔제지</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-09dc437c-e5b5-4e38-91b0-4f933d710e2d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9c591d44-3442-4eec-8508-1177c4a1d9ca\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-61d8a600-cc5b-47e8-aa6d-8937569b6bd4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c6c90376-fab4-4628-b0cd-8694b1b2bce8\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">아이보리 종이는 박스 중에 가장 많이 사용하는 종이입니다. 양면에 모두 인쇄를 할 수 있고 후면에도 거친 느낌이 아닌 깔끔한 느낌으로 표면이 처리되어 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1dc13450-92e5-435c-b67a-2ef97f0eb4ec\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223745219068/004.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-3e3dffe6-8030-4d65-9bee-945fbb5ede9b\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223745219068/005.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223745219068/006.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-81208cd2-6e53-4bdb-bf9a-bce42f271780\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-687c6b48-f355-4785-97f5-3eefe606da8a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-15160814-319d-4d02-8d3f-e6eff5c7330f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">· 색상 : 백색 / 후면 백색</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5d1c12d9-8325-4b6e-9cc5-2061d2e12c3a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a9e649cf-061d-4115-9c86-cf12092b3536\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">· 평량 : 280g, 300g, 350g, 400g, 450g, 500g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1f2a5f3e-3ac2-4ed1-af40-9775193faec0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-89744b13-a758-47f2-988d-7d3d9522427c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">· 용도 : 의류/잡화, 화장품/향수, 제약 등 고급 포장재 등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c6b3b4eb-9d6d-4b04-8900-94bd061219a7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4a031c15-982f-4e80-b07c-da4dc141546c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7364e782-14ff-400b-a271-a8a1c86aee43\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3b2ef8fb-5072-48d6-b098-29c883113d0b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>· 특징 : 이 종이는 단가와 퀄리티를 적절히 조합한 종이라고 말씀드립니다. 양면인쇄가 가능하면서도 인쇄가 안되는 후면도 깔끔하게 보임으로써 제품의 퀄리티를 의심하지 않는 종이라고 설명드립니다. 고급 화장품 등은 이 종이를 가장 많이 사용하며 두께도 다양하여 가장 사랑받는 종이라고 설명드립니다. 아이보리 중에 로열 아이보리는 더 고급스러움을 강조한 더 퀄리티 높은 종이입니다. 단가도 거의 70% 이상의 단가가 높게 처리되어 최고의 퀄리티를 보장합니다. 색상도 고백색이며 강도도 고탄력적이면서 텐션이 모두 탄탄하게 느껴집니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f3e93945-b5dd-45b0-b3fa-27617b0be79e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223745219068/007.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-80d79a98-6151-4f0c-9a51-4f10d9911cd0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3b6eb692-a75b-4374-9289-e8ca6c10596c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6b5911ba-4e4f-463d-9ead-cb34143d46a0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;background-color:#ffffff;\">* 로열 아이보리는 한 달간 꾸겨놓고 방치해도 탄력과 강도를 일정 부분은 유지하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3c15af46-d56b-4493-9cf4-7793c8a2a3e7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-abe9cd81-db29-4c78-87ac-47b9074899da\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-853aa24c-0a25-4847-8fc4-b2c63627da35\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-965fa2eb-01a1-4b6a-90f2-e8e699b943cc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-64f16f5e-7ac4-43b4-ab53-830e1a4d483e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d289c51d-30d2-4011-8fdd-3e2a59c96d20\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>를 가장 우선시합니다. 일반적으로 저렴하게 단가가 중요하게 차지하는 제품인 경우 이 종이를 선호합니다. 사전에 언급했듯이 일반 종이보다 약 75% 이상 저렴합니다. 일반적인 식품용기 중에 마닐라 종이가 가장 많으며 포장에 의미를 두는 경우 이 종이를 선택하세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-30dcc532-0d0a-4cc4-8e6b-438622829d53\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c9b12727-8851-4dab-930b-ac7d1db25398\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cf49ebcc-a8d4-456b-86f7-b62ca7dac748\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-82da9ec0-8a32-48d4-a69e-11cfab503f5e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>CCP</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c16c9c69-1547-4ee3-bd57-f55a28df8194\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b0b45804-df96-4892-afc2-6f1ace2ea61b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">ccp지는 기본적으로 표면에 코팅처리가 되어 있습니다. 유광 코팅처리가 되어 있어 탄탄하며 매끈하게 처리되어 있습니다. 반짝거리면서 탄탄한 느낌을 원하시면 ccp지를 선택해서 작업해 보세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1786c155-d6d7-41cd-89f5-7e88d1b309df\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223745219068/008.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b2ab2f93-8a68-44b3-b7dc-c30c99786dc0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2a97ed44-25da-4205-8d19-954c74c41eed\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d89dd6d1-074a-4e0b-8efb-6031a24089ff\" style=\"color:#ff0010;background-color:#ffffff;\">* 삼화페이지 샘플지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4fefec39-f84a-44ec-812a-07d7ba4ab915\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d98ac7df-0011-4d7e-8d85-6c5a223f9bde\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-58eb94c5-85ce-40a4-919a-fda8a4992cc0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0c011298-37c0-4700-ba46-b974ce3d3e12\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">· 색상 : 백색(유광코팅) / 후면 회색</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7e77f709-2cda-4966-8bfa-3d89b37bf12a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-23122727-d732-44a4-b004-c50c034f35f3\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">· 평량 : 250~400g/m²</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ed64dd65-6c19-4f88-9c81-4c1842eee4b6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-667b579d-c253-4d4c-8784-1242b7171c74\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">· 용도 : 고급 화장품, 고급 의약품, 고급 케이스 등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4483dd99-373c-4e5d-aef4-2b3c7f7007c0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}